Pre-Game Insights: Bangladesh and South Africa are set to face each other in their fifth match of the 2023 World Cup at Wankhede Stadium in Mumbai on 24 October 2023.
Bangladesh started strongly with a win against Afghanistan but has since faced consecutive defeats against England and New Zealand, followed by a loss to India.
South Africa began their campaign with wins against Sri Lanka, Australia, and England, showcasing their strong performance.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match will be free to watch on Disney+ Hotstar and Star Sports Network.
Star Sports Network holds the broadcast rights for the match in India.
